{"tid":852011,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"長頭髮真係好慘，夜晚都唔知洗唔洗頭好⋯⋯","createTime":"2018-10-07T14:11:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T14:51:01.000Z","uid":42927,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c127250c76dc52d7128e5a4377c72ac38bc43555","tid":852011,"uid":42927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T14:11:01.000Z","msg":"洗完又有排乾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n濕住瞓又唔得<br />\n唔洗又接受唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇絲打同我一樣成日諗住剪短啲頭髮<br />\n我都有諗過剪到掂膊頭嘅長度<br />\n(諗咗兩年都冇行動⋯⋯)<br />\n但最後都係唔捨得剪短，驚柒<br />\n而且留到咁長⋯⋯始終有啲感情<br />\n唉⋯⋯真係好煩"},{"pid":"64a31e55f709926afedb3119834cfc44afdd85f3","tid":852011,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T14:12:00.000Z","msg":"買個dyson吹頭會令你愛上吹頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bbdae1abf3f8e0d0ad5397827a59ad1fade2b56","tid":852011,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T14:24:00.000Z","msg":"通常要吹頭吹幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10f7dcf797dc90cf328052c9132bc9c755c372e3","tid":852011,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T14:25:19.000Z","msg":"買個靚風筒"},{"pid":"c755c96b94930e698d9ff28c9ca3b472daa3943c","tid":852011,"uid":71635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T14:31:57.000Z","msg":"剪薄會易乾"},{"pid":"1d903da84edafa12c82433a1c352d5f92c847b92","tid":852011,"uid":42927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bbdae1abf3f8e0d0ad5397827a59ad1fade2b56","tid":852011,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T14:24:00.000Z","msg":"通常要吹頭吹幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T14:37:17.000Z","msg":"其實又唔話好耐，可能我懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfdd8361d899865d22a6